        "created_at": "2017-07-10T04:24:11.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I have bought Ramonet in most vintages since 1989, even reaching back to older ones, but pricing of the g crus has pushed me back to the pricy premier crus. Hope Ruchottes is good!  Loved 01 at Ramonet. Thanks, Tom.</p>",
