        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"alan weinberg\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n alan weinberg:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I have bought Ramonet in most vintages since 1989, even reaching back to older ones, but pricing of the g crus has pushed me back to the pricy premier crus. Hope Ruchottes is good!  Loved 01 at Ramonet. Thanks, Tom.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Ugh.  Don\u2019t talk to me about ramonet 01s.  Nothing but brown soup from my case of batards.</p>",
