        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/dcornutt/{size}/562_2.png",
        "created_at": "2017-07-10T09:08:12.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The 2014 Ramonets are absolutely first level in white Burgundy.  I don\u2019t think I have tasted any others that even come close to them.   (I have tasted quite a few 2014 whites)</p>",
