        "name": "William Kelley",
        "username": "William_Kelley",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/william_kelley/{size}/2314_2.png",
        "created_at": "2017-07-10T13:06:32.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Nice notes. And agreed on the superlative quality of the 2014 Ramonet wines. Tasting them with Jean-Claude in January was one of the highlights of the vinous year, and as Don observes, not much comes close in 2014. The style of the domaine married perfectly with the vintage.</p>",
